item.description:
EVENT: We will take a leisurely walk around the Cleveland
Circle Reservoir and Streets nearby the Chestnut Hill Park. Ice Cream afterwards.

The Trip's Leader is Naomi and she can be reached at: (617-277-9968 by 9:30pm) or naomi.allen07@gmail.com An RSVP is Recommended
MEET: 1:30pm at the corner of Chestnut Hill Ave and Beacon Street near
the Reservoir. Rain Cancels.
COST: $5.00 for non-members
item.how_to_find_us: Contact Naomi at (617-277-9968 by 9:30pm or naomi.allen07@gmail.com for details
